{"tid":1404500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奧巴馬出力支持「烏克蘭革命」, 封殺濫權官員, 派員探望示威者","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:38:42.000Z","uid":134071,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0676c6a5899c60b83f2c59dfe2b16b54bf7528","tid":1404500,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:50:52.000Z","msg":"外國勢力對抗爭運動成敗重要. &nbsp;「烏克蘭革命」的成功, 奧巴馬唔係無做野.<br />\n<br />\n在2013件12月, 奧巴馬已親自派遣特使去烏克蘭探望示威者. (而且特使仲係以Obama admin的身份去探望示威者.)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbsnews.com/news/us-victoria-nuland-wades-into-ukraine-turmoil-over-yanukovich/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fus-victoria-nuland-wades-into-ukraine-turmoil-over-yanukovich%2F&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=d2e11215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbsnews.com/news/us-victoria-nuland-wades-into-ukraine-turmoil-over-yanukovich/</a><br />\n<br />\n在2014年2月, 奧巴馬警告烏克蘭軍隊不得介入示威, 否則美國將追究責任. 他又指政府對妥善對待示威者負有主要責任.<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20140220/s00005/1392858058750\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20140220%2Fs00005%2F1392858058750&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=33593da6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20140220%2Fs00005%2F1392858058750&h=169f70af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20140220/s00005/1392858058750</a><br />\n<br />\n在2014年2月, 美國並落實封殺20名烏克蘭濫權官員, 主要理由係佢地粗暴對待示威者.<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/02/us-imposes-visa-ban-on-20-ukrainians-over-euromaidan-riots/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.biharprabha.com%2F2014%2F02%2Fus-imposes-visa-ban-on-20-ukrainians-over-euromaidan-riots%2F&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=e3e0f492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.biharprabha.com/2014/02/us-imposes-visa-ban-on-20-ukrainians-over-euromaidan-riots/</a><br />\n<br />\n不過, 奧巴馬始終有著左膠式軟弱.  特朗普批評奧巴馬要為烏克蘭最後的分裂(失去&quot;克里米亞&quot;)負責任.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rferl.org/a/trump-blames-obama-regime-for-ukraine-s-loss-of-crimea/29588249.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rferl.org%2Fa%2Ftrump-blames-obama-regime-for-ukraine-s-loss-of-crimea%2F29588249.html&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=a33c5a83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rferl.org/a/trump-blames-obama-regime-for-ukraine-s-loss-of-crimea/29588249.html</a>"},{"pid":"327dab11fda6957fcaac9b8b1affcbed46273362","tid":1404500,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:52:04.000Z","msg":"不過, 奧巴馬無話示威係riots<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/oZtdEV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZtdEV7.jpg&h=03881b18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8172ad03571a0ae98410f44acfc6f9c079211a80","tid":1404500,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d1b120163401ff8b09392b0c479e859b1cc628","tid":1404500,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:56:17.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"0d90d96665ed9c84cf6a83bcee2650aea2e6ee4a","tid":1404500,"uid":34877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"最大貢獻咪派左個大使去傾<br />\n之後沒有了<br />\n示威死咗200人之後比俄羅斯入侵死6000人"},{"pid":"e3f087fb2c3937b5f08fb1128fb277cd76167ec2","tid":1404500,"uid":34334,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d24d44641f4ba6017acdbe61acad7451146e73ea","tid":1404500,"uid":2732